videos.description: Elissa Cunane scores 11 points in the first quarter to give NC State a lead over Virginia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (Elissa Cunane puts NC State on top early with 11-point first quarter) 2022/2/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Elissa Cunane puts NC State on top early with 11-point first quarter

videos.description: Aisha Sheppard and Cayla King sink 3-pointers on back-to-back possessions to bring Virginia Tech within a point of NC State.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Virginia Tech storms back with consecutive triples) 2022/2/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Virginia Tech storms back with consecutive triples

videos.description: NC State extends its lead heading into the fourth quarter thanks to an offensive rebound and putback by Jada Boyd.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Jada Boyd beats the third-quarter buzzer for NC State) 2022/2/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jada Boyd beats the third-quarter buzzer for NC State

videos.description: After Georgia Amoore hits a game-tying layup for Virginia Tech, Elissa Cunane scores on the other end to give NC State the lead again.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (NC State takes late lead as Cunane responds to VT's clutch basket) 2022/2/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: NC State takes late lead as Cunane responds to VT's clutch basket

videos.description: NC State hangs on late to beat Virginia Tech, clinching the program's first outright ACC regular season title since 1990.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (NC State survives at the buzzer to clinch ACC regular season title) 2022/2/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: NC State survives at the buzzer to clinch ACC regular season title
